title: CESAR MILLAN, THE DOG WHISPERER - IMPAULSIVE EP. 97
itunes:title: CESAR MILLAN, THE DOG WHISPERER - IMPAULSIVE EP. 97
description:
The boys are tamed by TV legend Cesar Millan, the world’s best and most renowned dog trainer. When he was a teenager, César jumped the Mexican-American border and was homeless during his first stay in America. Today, after decades of television success and 25 years of canine experience, Cesar resides on his own, personal mountain.
